      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in exemplary mechanical and aesthetic condition. This specimen features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a 11.5:1 compression ratio to deliver linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The VANOS system has been meticulously serviced, and the rear subframe\u2014a known structural point\u2014has been inspected and found to be in factory-perfect condition. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to an M-Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The suspension maintains its original geometry and damping rates, providing the telepathic handling characteristics the E46 chassis is renowned for. This is a turn-key enthusiast piece with no modifications, representing the pinnacle of naturally aspirated M-division engineering.",
